## 9. Comparison Table

| Feature | unique_ptr | shared_ptr | weak_ptr |
|---|---|---|---|
| Ownership | Exclusive | Shared | None |
| Copyable | No | Yes | Yes |
| Movable | Yes | Yes | Yes |
| Ref count overhead | No | Yes | Yes |
| Breaks cycles | — | No | Yes |
| Needs .lock() | No | No | Yes |
| Thread-safe ref count | — | Yes | Yes |
| Runtime performance | Zero overhead | Slight overhead | Slight overhead |

